eturn\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 675}, {\"ngram\": \"the gymnastics arena\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 699}, {\"ngram\": \"her first Olympic gold\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"his remarkable diving legacy\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"synchro silver\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The medal ceremonies that follow those dramatic moments on the field of play is when the sense of achievement really starts to sink in.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 983, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The medal ceremonies\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 868}, {\"ngram\": \"those dramatic moments\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 903}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"play\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 924}, {\"ngram\": \"the sense\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"achievement\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 957}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, time and time again, we see athletes biting their gold, silver and bronze medals.\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1070, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \"their gold, silver and bronze medals\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a practice as common and ingrained in the Olympics as some of the sports themselves - but why do they do it?\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1185, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a practice\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1127}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back in the day, one of the ways to determine whether the shiny metal in your hand was gold was to bite into it, as gold is softer and more malleable than other metals.\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"the ways\", \"from\": 1211, 